<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="abc.css"><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" /><h1>Investors Bank on the Appeal of a Startup"s Design-Focused Office Products</h1>
								
									<div class="h5n text-medgrey">
						This story appears in the <a>2012</a> issue of <a><em>Entrepreneur</em></a>. <a>Subscribe »</a>
					</div>
				
				
										
					
	
	<div class="articleimg" style="width: 250px;"><img alt=""We believe it's an open market for beautiful products." <br>
--J. Christopher Burch, Poppin" src="//assets.entrepreneur.com/article/poppin-j-christopher-burch.jpg" style="float: right; width: 250px; height: 351px; " />
<div class="caption">"We believe it's an open market for beautiful products." --J. Christopher Burch, Poppin</div>
